{
  "texts": [
    "This section reports the model performance, initially from a purely numerical perspective.",
    "Later, we will translate this information back into maps and evaluate their temporal characteristics.",
    "Figure 7 offers an overview of the performance that our ENN returned for its two components.",
    "The left panel reports an AUC of 0.93, associated with an F1 Score of 0.96 and IOU of 0.95.",
    "This predictive performance complies with the classification performance of outstanding data-driven models (Hosmer and Lemeshow, 2000)."
  ]
}